2019-12-16 12:20:42	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> like
2019-12-16 12:20:54	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> ```computer = Computer.new ⏎ computer.drive = Drive.dvd ⏎ ...``` [https://gitter.im/crystal-lang/crystal?at=5df7d9167ce7ea1e35968856]
