2019-12-16 16:32:32	FromGitter	<bew> great PR! now my crystal hello world only depends on: ⏎  ⏎ ```code paste, see link``` ⏎  ⏎ Do you have any idea why I have a dep on gcc? [https://gitter.im/crystal-lang/crystal?at=5df814107ce7ea1e35984108]
2019-12-16 16:33:45	FromGitter	<manveru> `nix why-depends ./result /nix/store/c6jvs50xrcy2m1nbrmpjwad51f62fcrx-gcc-8.3.0`
2019-12-16 16:37:42	FromGitter	<bew> hmm... there a reference (in the binary's strings) to: ⏎  ⏎ ```code paste, see link``` [https://gitter.im/crystal-lang/crystal?at=5df8154655d9392300229d4a]
2019-12-16 16:39:39	FromGitter	<manveru> hmm, not sure why they're needed, maybe try compiling with `--no-debug`?
2019-12-16 16:40:25	FromGitter	<manveru> those files are used for finding beginning/end of constructors, possibly some ffi thing?
2019-12-16 16:40:37	FromGitter	<bew> just tried with --no-debug & --release, same
2019-12-16 16:41:15	FromGitter	<manveru> normally those should be in `gcc.lib`, and not `gcc`
2019-12-16 16:41:35	FromGitter	<manveru> which is way lighter, can you share how you build it atm?
2019-12-16 16:44:06	FromGitter	<bew> ```code paste, see link``` ⏎  ⏎ Simplest derivation I think, with a `puts "Hello from Nix"` in `hello.cr` [https://gitter.im/crystal-lang/crystal?at=5df816c555d939230022aad4]
2019-12-16 16:44:25	FromGitter	<manveru> yeah, please use `crystal.buildCrystalPackage` for that
2019-12-16 16:44:54	FromGitter	<manveru> `stdenv.mkDerivation` implicitly pulls in the full `gcc`, which ends up being the one being referenced
2019-12-16 16:45:11	FromGitter	<bew> Oo
2019-12-16 16:45:29	FromGitter	<manveru> it's usually used for building C/C++, so it makes sense :)
2019-12-16 16:48:42	FromGitter	<bew> but you're also using `stdenv.mkDerivation` in `crystal.buildCrystalPackage` ..?
2019-12-16 16:51:08	FromGitter	<manveru> you're right... i somehow thought i had a different result
2019-12-16 16:54:43	FromGitter	<bew> we also have a dep on glibc (~30MB) just for ld-linux... would be nice to have a separate output for this single thing that ~ every packages need, to really have a few KB worth of deps
2019-12-16 16:54:47	FromGitter	<manveru> https://i.imgur.com/uYxla1M.png
2019-12-16 16:55:20	FromGitter	<manveru> that's my dependency graph for `crystal2nix` without `nix-prefetch-git`
2019-12-16 16:55:29	FromGitter	<bew> pretty nice
2019-12-16 16:55:40	FromGitter	<manveru> so it clearly uses `gcc-lib`, not `gcc`
