2019-12-16 16:56:27	FromGitter	<bew> why?
2019-12-16 16:56:37	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> for using the `XML` module
2019-12-16 16:56:48	FromGitter	<manveru> only if you require it
2019-12-16 16:57:06	FromGitter	<Blacksmoke16> ah so it sees you required it then includes that dep?
2019-12-16 16:57:47	FromGitter	<manveru> testing :)
2019-12-16 16:58:05	FromGitter	<manveru> jup
2019-12-16 16:58:13	FromGitter	<bew> not exactly, it sees that the final binary needs it after the build, so it includes that dep
